# Linux Commands to manage Local Accounts:
# useradd <options> <username/login> --> create new user
# userdel <options> <username/login> --> delete user
# usermod <options> <username/login> --> modify user
# passwd <username/login> --> assign new password to user
# chage <options> <username/login> --> modify user password expiry information.
